responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "4BF1239B4D14D720903BF6AD0A766EF0", "We have sustained significant losses and we hope that none have suffered fates worse than death. Many wraiths have grown bolder in the fallout of the blast and Viscount Harrken remains to be accounted for among the dead or living.")
